#. Translators: This is the label for the Numpad Nav Mode settings category in NVDA Settings panel.
#. Add-on summary, usually the user visible name of the addon.
#. Translators: Summary for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in Add-ons Manager.
msgid "Numpad Nav Mode"
msgstr "Navigationsmodus über den Nummernblock"

#. Translators: The label for a checkbox in Numpad Nav Mode settings panel
msgid "Start NVDA with the numpad set to Windows nav mode"
msgstr ""
"Starten Sie NVDA mit dem Navigationsmodus eingestellten Nummernblock In "
"Windows"

#. Translators: Label of the list which allows configuring initial numlock state
msgid "State of numlock when NVDA starts or profile loads"
msgstr ""
"Zustand des Nummernblocks beim Starten von NVDA oder beim Laden des Profils"

#. Translators: Option not to change numlock state when NVDA starts/profile is loaded
msgid "Do not change"
msgstr "Nicht ändern"

#. Translators: Option to turn numlock off when NVDA starts/profile is loaded
msgid "Turn numlock off"
msgstr "Nummernblock ausschalten"

#. Translators: Option to turn numlock on when NVDA starts/profile is loaded
msgid "Turn numlock on"
msgstr "Nummernblock einschalten"

#. Translators: The label for a checkbox in Numpad Nav Mode settings panel
msgid "Initial numlock state is configuration profile dependent"
msgstr ""
"Der anfängliche Status des Nummernblocks ist abhängig vom "
"Konfigurationsprofil"

#. Translators: returned as part of some user messages
msgid "NVDA"
msgstr "NVDA"

#. Translators: returned as part of some user messages
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Windows"

#. Translators: description of the Numpad Nav Mode toggle gesture for keyboard help
msgid ""
"Toggles the numpad between NVDA navigation and Windows navigation modes."
msgstr ""
"Schaltet den Nummernblock zwischen dem Navigationsmodus von NVDA und Windows "
"um."

#. Translators: message given to the user when the numpad's mode changes between NVDA and Windows nav
#. Note: the variable given to format() is already translated.
msgid "Numpad mode {}."
msgstr "Status des Nummernblocks {}."

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-ons manager
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Allows switching the numpad between NVDA navigation mode, and Windows "
"navigation mode.\n"
"Especially useful if migrating from Jaws; or for laptop users preferring "
"laptop mode, but who have a numpad and want to use it for arrow keys, etc.\n"
"The add-on also gives control of numlock state when starting NVDA or "
"changing profiles."
msgstr ""
"Schaltet den Nummernblock zwischen dem Navigationsmodus von NVDA und Windows "
"um.\n"
"Besonders nützlich bei der Umstellung von JAWS; oder für Laptop-Benutzer, "
"die den Laptop-Modus bevorzugen, aber einen Nummernblock haben und ihn für "
"Pfeiltasten, etc. verwenden möchten.\n"
"Die NVDA-Erweiterung ermöglicht auch die Kontrolle über den Status des "
"Nummernblocks beim Starten von NVDA oder beim Wechsel des Profils..."
